{"tid":1349583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔洗講野 光復元朗呢單野事在必行","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:44:21.000Z","uid":147159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88e8b82ff8167a70c77e85e8f8f058d067e31476","tid":1349583,"uid":147159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"我成家都深藍親中 <br />\n未發生琴晚單嘢之前 一直都係屌緊啲示威者<br />\n淨係會睇無線新聞 話香港啲學生冇嘢搵嘢嚟搞<br />\n一起身睇完啲片 個個都話 <br />\n原來政府咁仆街 差佬又選擇性執法 <br />\n唔怪得班學生上街抗爭<br />\n仲話林鄭啊 何君堯啊呢啲仆街 搵人劈死佢<br />\n證明而家已經冇藍黃之分 只有黑白之分<br />\n大家槍頭已經對準 黑警 政府 黑社會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家都留意番上環單野 好多兄弟都受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好放棄啊 只要堅持落去我哋一定得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232a56d34cb419217eedcc2c06309d382ab61adb","tid":1349583,"uid":192059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654a1aa2ca3091493ec5068aa3f4270db0d2fd28","tid":1349583,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰今日繼續提供義載 睇下有冇巴打需要<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/doeigT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/doeigT</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}